Zombies are generic monsters found throughout Gielinor as a result of Necromancers reanimating their bodies, just like Skeletons. This means they count as undead NPCs and are weak to the effects of both the Salve amulet and the Crumble Undead spell.

Most zombies will be low level, hence serving as a decent training method for low-levelled players.
